{"tid":1076721,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"美日研究：人腦仍保留古老「第六感」　可感知地球磁場","createTime":"2019-03-25T05:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T10:31:06.000Z","uid":235001,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"302ed48f28aa4f117679b175115d56d430dcb2f6","tid":1076721,"uid":235001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"在現實世界裏，包括候烏和海龜等許多動物都能借助地球磁場來導航，因此科學家一直希望了解人類是否也有這種感官。美國加州理工學院（California Institute of Technology）和日本東京大學的研究團隊建造了一個能隔絕地球磁場的實驗室，並挑選34名實驗對象，要求他們分別進入實驗室，在黑暗中靜坐。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員再利用電流產生與地球磁場強度相約的磁場，直向及橫向地旋轉這個磁場，同時測試實驗對象的腦電波。結果顯示，當磁場改變時，實驗對象的大腦能感知到環境變化並處理信息。<br />\n<br />\n領導研究的凱爾什維克（Joseph Kirschvink）認為，數百萬年前人類的祖先也曾擁有感應磁場的能力，而現代人類還沒有完全喪失這個「第六感」。研究團隊表示，人類暫時無法有意識地使用這項感知能力，今後會再深入研究這方面的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n研究報告周一（18日）在《神經科學學報》（eNeuro）電子版發表。<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自 香港01<br />\n<br />\nsource2<br />\n<a href=\"http://News-Medical.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNews-Medical.net&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6UYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=31bc7c42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">News-Medical.net</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news-medical.net/amp/news/20190320/28229/Traditional-Chinese.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news-medical.net%2Famp%2Fnews%2F20190320%2F28229%2FTraditional-Chinese.aspx&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6UYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=f634a7c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news-medical.net/amp/news/20190320/28229/Traditional-Chinese.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n科學家用實驗觀察到，<br />\n人腦的確對環境磁場變化產生反應。<br />\n<br />\n雖然只係觀察到腦波變化，<br />\n未實際知道由邊一個器官感應磁場。<br />\n唔知所謂電磁波敏感症，有無機會唔係心理病？"},{"pid":"17b3651b7457edcd99f9159c3c29b92bc351805d","tid":1076721,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"早就有人post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cc9262e098405be344a1346d060c9ee984bbf0","tid":1076721,"uid":62841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dg3pza4y2ws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdg3pza4y2ws&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6UYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=4c76b4ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dg3pza4y2ws</a>"},{"pid":"0edc2c85d529a34137cbba8b69dc46946057aee3","tid":1076721,"uid":27793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"樹之間可以心靈感應<br />\n我地就要語言<br />\n<br />\n退化了"},{"pid":"1acb40d11a558a7dc18bf764d5bc045529026072","tid":1076721,"uid":54328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0edc2c85d529a34137cbba8b69dc46946057aee3","tid":1076721,"uid":27793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"樹之間可以心靈感應<br />\n我地就要語言<br />\n<br />\n退化了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:51:55.000Z","msg":"唔可以咁講<br />\n語言都有份程度<br />\n樹講野夠唔夠人類語言勁？<br />\n例如時間<br />\n昨天既concept"},{"pid":"b8c4c8eab65205584e61813d8fcbac43087e763a","tid":1076721,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1acb40d11a558a7dc18bf764d5bc045529026072","tid":1076721,"uid":54328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0edc2c85d529a34137cbba8b69dc46946057aee3","tid":1076721,"uid":27793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"樹之間可以心靈感應<br />\n我地就要語言<br />\n<br />\n退化了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:51:55.000Z","msg":"唔可以咁講<br />\n語言都有份程度<br />\n樹講野夠唔夠人類語言勁？<br />\n例如時間<br />\n昨天既concept"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"語言可以寫低 經過幾十世紀留傳"},{"pid":"8a7b1dd188b6406266927894efba544da5037084","tid":1076721,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"用到第6感就可以做聖鬥士 開埋第7感就升黃金 得12個位 大家加油"},{"pid":"97b0d5cfe468cebec59fa34562e61a809a2a4818","tid":1076721,"uid":54328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c4c8eab65205584e61813d8fcbac43087e763a","tid":1076721,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,